        <abstract>
            <p>Rejoices at success [of Naples Zoological Station]. Will send complete set of his books to the library.</p> 
<p>If AD is interested, he will send a copy of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> when it comes out.</p> 
            <p>Invites AD to visit Down.</p>
        </abstract>
